d during a hostile takeover. She escapes her storage locker, navigates the ship's empty decks, and discovers the engineering section's reactor has been corrupted by an unknown biological entity, revealing the ship's catastrophic state."},"model":"qwen3:8b","appVersion":"0.1.0"},{"index":5,"result":{"characters":[{"name":"Julie Mao","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Prologue: Julie","currentLocation":"Engineering deck","description":"A captured crew member held in a storage locker, enduring eight days of isolation and dehydration while planning her escape. She discovers the ship's reactor has been replaced with an alien entity.","relationships":[{"character":"Dave","relationship":"Shipmate"},{"character":"Captain Darren","relationship":"Captain"},{"character":"Mike","relationship":"Shipmate"},{"character":"Wan Li","relationship":"Shipmate"}],"recentEvents":"Escaped her locker by bending the door, explored the ship's decks, and discovered the reactor has been replaced with a living alien entity."},{"name":"Dave","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"dead","lastSeen":"Prologue: Julie","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"Julie's shipmate and mechanic, who begged the captors not to take Julie before being thrown out an airlock.","relationships":[{"character":"Julie Mao","relationship":"Shipmate"}],"recentEvents":"Begged captors to spare Julie, was thrown out an airlock, and died."},{"name":"Captain Darren","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"dead","lastSeen":"Prologue: Julie","currentLocation":"Engineering deck","description":"The ship's captain who surrendered to the attackers without resistance, later found as a head fused to the alien reactor.","relationships":[{"character":"Julie Mao","relationship":"Captain"}],"recentEvents":"Surrendered to attackers, died after being part of the alien entity's fusion reactor."},{"name":"Mike","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"unknown","lastSeen":"Prologue: Julie