 limb.","relationships":[{"character":"Shed Garvey","relationship":"Crewmate"}],"recentEvents":"Implied to have an injured arm, mentioned by Shed during the aftermath."},{"name":"Ade Tukunbo","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter Five: Holden","currentLocation":"Knight","description":"Navigator with a Nigerian accent and a fondness for music. Has a flirtatious relationship with Holden.","relationships":[{"character":"Jim Holden","relationship":"Romantic interest"}],"recentEvents":"Attempted to power up the Knight's drive, survived the nuke blast, communicated with Holden during the crisis."},{"name":"Rebecca Byers","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter One: Holden","currentLocation":"Canterbury","description":"Comm officer with a sharp appearance and a history of legal troubles. Handles emergency communications.","relationships":[{"character":"Captain McDowell","relationship":"Subordinate"}],"recentEvents":"Received and relayed the emergency signal from an unknown ship."},{"name":"Captain McDowell","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter Five: Holden","currentLocation":"Knight","description":"Commanding officer of the Canterbury. A grizzled veteran with a distrust of corrective surgery.","relationships":[{"character":"Jim Holden","relationship":"Former subordinate"}],"recentEvents":"Gave Holden instructions for the broadcast operation"},{"name":"Detective Miller","aliases":["Miller"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter Eight: Miller","currentLocation":"Ceres","description":"A seasoned detective working for Star Helix Security on Ceres, known for his poker skills and ability to interpret underworld slang.","relationships":[{"character":"Dmitri Havelock","relationship":"Partner"},{"character":"Captain Shaddid","relationship":"Superior"}],"recentEvents":"Investigated Julie Mao's case, discussed transfer to Ganymede, observed station tensions"},{"