 McDowell","relationship":"Subordinate"}],"recentEvents":"Received and relayed the emergency signal from an unknown ship."},{"name":"Captain McDowell","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter Five: Holden","currentLocation":"Knight","description":"Commanding officer of the Canterbury. A grizzled veteran with a distrust of corrective surgery.","relationships":[{"character":"Jim Holden","relationship":"Former subordinate"}],"recentEvents":"Gave Holden instructions for the broadcast operation"},{"name":"Detective Miller [aliases: Miller]","aliases":["Miller","Detective Miller"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter Thirty-Eight: Miller","currentLocation":"Tycho Station","description":"Experienced security officer with a troubled past, investigating Julie Mao's disappearance while navigating political tensions between Mars, the Belt, and Earth.","relationships":[{"character":"Dmitri Havelock","relationship":"Former partner"},{"character":"Captain Shaddid","relationship":"Superior"},{"character":"Juliette Andromeda Mao","relationship":"OPA contact"},{"character":"Havelock","relationship":"Partner who covers for Miller's absence"},{"character":"Octavia Muss","relationship":"Partner"},{"character":"Julie Mao","relationship":"Subject of investigation"},{"character":"Muss","relationship":"Partner"},{"character":"Shaddid","relationship":"Superior"},{"character":"Dawes","relationship":"Colleague"},{"character":"Inspector Sematimba","relationship":"Contacted for police assistance"},{"character":"Jim Holden","relationship":"Captain of the Rocinante, debates with Miller about broadcasting the protomolecule data"},{"character":"Naomi Nagata","relationship":"Aboard the Rocinante, with whom Miller discusses ethical dilemmas"},{"character":"Sematimba","relationship":"Contacted police"},{"character":"Amos Burton","relationship":"Team member"},{"character":"Alex Kamal","relationship":"Crewmate"}],"recentEvents":"Discussed coordinates for 